Hello! Thank you for contacting RT 6 Boozers. My name is Sarah, and I'm here to help you today.

Hi Sarah, I'm looking for some information about your bar.

Of course! I'd be happy to assist you. May I have your name, please?

Sure! My name is John.

Great to meet you, John! How can I assist you today regarding our services?

I was wondering about your happy hour specials.

Happy hour is from four PM to six PM every weekday. Would you like to know about our drink specials as well?

Yes, please! And I would like to reserve a table for my friends.

Absolutely! I can help with that. Could you please provide me with your phone number, spelled out?

It’s nine eight seven, six five four, three two one zero.

Thank you, John! Lastly, could you provide your email address for confirmation?

Sure, it’s john.doe@example.com.

Thank you for that information! I will send you a confirmation shortly. Is there anything else I can help you with?

No, that will be all for now. Thanks!

You're welcome! Thank you for your time, John. Have a great day, and we look forward to seeing you at RT 6 Boozers!
